12.name: welcome
12.html:
Welcome!

Values:

Mean

Depending on selected distribution it will set:

  • Exponential, normal, erlang: mean
  • Uniform: min

Deviation

Depending on selected distribution it will set:

  • Constant, exponential: nothing (can be left empty)
  • Normal: deviation
  • Erlang: k value
  • Uniform: max


Shortkeys:

Delete == Remove selected node

Mouse Left Click == Move

Mouse Right == Delete Option

Ctrl + Wheel == Zoom
